Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,适应\N{\fs24\1c}Adapt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是人类的本能 对吧\N{\fs24\1c}That's what humans do, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的大优势\N{\fs24\1c}Our great leg up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们摸爬滚打\N{\fs24\1c}We roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们见招拆招\N{\fs24\1c}We hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬紧牙关 随机应变\N{\fs24\1c}Knuckle down and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪国列车也是一种适应\N{\fs24\1c}Even Snowpiercer is an adaptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.67,0:00:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德就是如此\N{\fs24\1c}That was classic Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界冰封时\N{\fs24\1c}While the world froze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他巨富都想在地堡里躲避末日\N{\fs24\1c}and the other mega-rich tried to hole up in bunkers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是上传他们的意识\N{\fs24\1c}or upload their consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.18,0:00:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生却翻出了他的旧火车\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford dusted off his train set.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪国列车是他的系统\N{\fs24\1c}Snowpiercer is His system.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统抗拒改变\N{\fs24\1c}Systems resist change,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.83,0:01:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕没有缔造者的干预\N{\fs24\1c}even without their maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是个科学家\N{\fs24\1c}I'm just a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来拯救世界 不是改变它的\N{\fs24\1c}I'm here to save the world, not change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.99,0:01:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们的生存机会渺茫\N{\fs24\1c}I know our chances of surviving are slim at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而对此 我也只能\N{\fs24\1c}All I can do about that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在雪国列车上制造片刻的幸福\N{\fs24\1c}is provide small moments of happiness on Snowpiercer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:41.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这1001节车厢里\N{\fs24\1c}1,001 cars long.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord1\fs33\b1}雪国列车\N第一季 第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:08.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道还醒着\N{\fs24\1c}I knew you'd be up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳者无休\N{\fs24\1c}No rest for the weary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs24\1c}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你照顾好自己 梅\N{\fs24\1c}I need you to take care of yourself, Mel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.58,0:02:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不能病倒\N{\fs24\1c}We can't afford you getting sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.19,0:02:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,供给链的问题越来越严重\N{\fs24\1c}There's mounting supply-chain issues,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在还要自己侦办谋杀案吗\N{\fs24\1c}and now you're taking this murder investigation on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你担心\N{\fs24\1c}I appreciate your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的\N{\fs24\1c}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的事吗\N{\fs24\1c}Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有\N{\fs24\1c}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你去求助\N{\fs24\1c}I want you to ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮我\N{\fs24\1c}Help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 醒醒\N{\fs24\1c}Layton, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们需要你 -发生了什么\N{\fs24\1c}- We need you. - What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:02:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会看到的\N{\fs24\1c}You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想到甲烷短缺的\N{\fs24\1c}So, have you thought of a workaround
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决办法了吗\N{\fs24\1c}for the methane shortage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.68,0:03:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs24\1c}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山羊屁\N{\fs24\1c}Goat farts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs24\1c}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻省理工学院\N{\fs24\1c}MIT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道没白上\N{\fs24\1c}I knew it would pay off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮·卡维尔\N{\fs24\1c}Melanie Cavill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怕被人看到在一起\N{\fs24\1c}I'm not afraid to be seen together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是早上不想跟我一起去上班\N{\fs24\1c}You just don't want to walk to work with me in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍珠 关于我的传闻现在够多了\N{\fs24\1c}Jinju, there's enough track talk about me as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须挺身而出 宝贝\N{\fs24\1c}Hey, you got to step up for this, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚不都挺身了吗\N{\fs24\1c}Isn't that what I just did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, you did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的 但...\N{\fs24\1c}And I will. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我点时间\N{\fs24\1c}Give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三等厢人对于跟前车厢的人约会很别扭\N{\fs24\1c}Thirdies are weird about dating uptrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是前车厢还是后车厢有什么不同\N{\fs24\1c}What's the difference whether it's uptrain or downtrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是二等厢的\N{\fs24\1c}You're from Second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是身处特权才会这么想\N{\fs24\1c}You have the privilege of seeing it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝 我知道你不为之所动\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, baby, I know you're not enticed by all this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你来自底特律\N{\fs24\1c}'cause you're from Detroit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来自旧金山\N{\fs24\1c}I'm from San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些地方都消失了\N{\fs24\1c}Those places are gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在重新开始的担子落在了我们肩上\N{\fs24\1c}but now it's up to us to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,农业员\N{\fs24\1c}Agricultural Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮基·吉奈特死了\N{\fs24\1c}Nikki Genet is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾\N{\fs24\1c}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你有多在乎她\N{\fs24\1c}I know how much you cared for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 别哭了\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了 亨利\N{\fs24\1c}Stop it, Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给你个机会向威尔福德先生赎罪\N{\fs24\1c}I'm gonna give you a chance to make things right with Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\fs24\1c}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你去拿一台轮床和一些床单\N{\fs24\1c}I want you to go get a gurney and some sheets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让任何人看到她\N{\fs24\1c}Don't let anyone see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要验尸数据\N{\fs24\1c}We need postmortem data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我要让你做什么吗\N{\fs24\1c}Do you understand what I'm asking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道\N{\fs24\1c}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会为我去做吗 亨利\N{\fs24\1c}Will you do that for me, Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪了\N{\fs24\1c}Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说了一个头等厢杀手的长相\N{\fs24\1c}I gave you a description of a First Class killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又做了什么\N{\fs24\1c}What did you do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想等到早晨\N{\fs24\1c}I was waiting till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头等厢的人就能等到早上\N{\fs24\1c}First waits till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她死了 杀手却还能吃到培根鸡蛋\N{\fs24\1c}She's dead -- our killer gets his bacon and eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 莱顿 我们都辜负了她\N{\fs24\1c}Shut up, Layton. We all failed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边境关闭了\N{\fs24\1c}The border's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚从二等厢过来\N{\fs24\1c}I just came from Second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搏击赛开始之后就关了\N{\fs24\1c}It's been closed since the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀手来自头等厢\N{\fs24\1c}The killer's from First.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他跟着你 他提前离开了搏击赛\N{\fs24\1c}If he followed you, he left the fight early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间去前厢\N{\fs24\1c}No time to get uptrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么他还在三等厢\N{\fs24\1c}Then he's still in Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fs24\1c}How we doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换到早餐部来了\N{\fs24\1c}Switching to breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列车一圈圈走着\N{\fs24\1c}'Round and 'round she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想喝最后一瓶"铁路工啤酒"吗\N{\fs24\1c}You want one last Railman's?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了\N{\fs24\1c}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他们还要把边境关多久吗\N{\fs24\1c}Any word how long they're keeping that damn border closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们想的话 关一晚上都行\N{\fs24\1c}They'll close it all night if they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搏击赛一片混乱\N{\fs24\1c}That fight was a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来自哪里\N{\fs24\1c}Where you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二等厢\N{\fs24\1c}Second?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是头等舱的酒水代币\N{\fs24\1c}Hey, these are First Class booze tokens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs24\1c}I mean... thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.62,0:07:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前厢有多少人\N{\fs24\1c}Alright, how many men do you have uptrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多\N{\fs24\1c}We've got plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从车尾派一支搜索队到前厢\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, send a sweep team uptrain from the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看了 小子\N{\fs24\1c}Eyes up, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来交给我们\N{\fs24\1c}We've got it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿先生不必看到这个 对吗\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Layton doesn't really need to see this, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们甚至不知道自己在找谁\N{\fs24\1c}They don't even know who they're chasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要去头等厢\N{\fs24\1c}I need to go to First.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不能踏入头等厢一步\N{\fs24\1c}He doesn't set one foot in First.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他听从威尔福德先生的命令\N{\fs24\1c}He does whatever Mr. Wilford wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fs24\1c}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.22,0:07:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把所有去观看了搏击赛的头等厢乘客都叫醒\N{\fs24\1c}Let's get every First Class passenger that was at the fight out of bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会很不受欢迎\N{\fs24\1c}That will not be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受欢迎\N{\fs24\1c}Popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这有个连环杀人犯\N{\fs24\1c}You people have a serial killer --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,低调点 好吗\N{\fs24\1c}Tone it down, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得知道搜索开始了\N{\fs24\1c}I need to know that the search is underway,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你和我去头等厢\N{\fs24\1c}and then you and I will go to First.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要等威尔福德先生同意\N{\fs24\1c}You have to clear that with Mr. Wilford,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你能决定\N{\fs24\1c}or is that your call?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等你准备好 我要跟她谈谈\N{\fs24\1c}When you're ready, I'll be talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的司闸员会从这开始工作\N{\fs24\1c}Alright, my Brakemen will work down from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打开每扇门 检查所有橱柜\N{\fs24\1c}We'll open every door. We'll check every cupboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后去中部的农业区和我的人汇合\N{\fs24\1c}And meet my men in the middle at Ag-Sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从车尾派一支搜索队到前厢\N{\fs24\1c}Start a sweep team uptrain from the Tail, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们检查所有...\N{\fs24\1c}From there, we will review all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.85,0:08:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那附属列车呢\N{\fs24\1c}What about the subtrain?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是禁止非必要人员进入\N{\fs24\1c}It's still closed to nonessential personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是会派一支巡逻队过去\N{\fs24\1c}I'll put another patrol down there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没被停职吗\N{\fs24\1c}He's not suspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们人手不够 需要所有人\N{\fs24\1c}We're shorthanded. We need every man we've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在走私克洛诺 -他是你的搭档\N{\fs24\1c}- He was slinging Kroney. - He's your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在和好 晚点和好 随便你\N{\fs24\1c}Work it out now. Work it out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之要做好你的工作 去吧\N{\fs24\1c}Just do your freakin' job. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请节哀\N{\fs24\1c}I'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果凶手是头等厢的人\N{\fs24\1c}If the killer's from First,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你只能调查到这了\N{\fs24\1c}they'll only let you get so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮基将永远讨不回公道\N{\fs24\1c}and there won't be any justice for Nikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三等厢的人会怎么想\N{\fs24\1c}How's Third gonna take that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个受害者都出自那里\N{\fs24\1c}Both victims are theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就要拭目以待了 警探\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, that remains to be seen, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.62,0:09:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我知道你在这是做什么的了\N{\fs24\1c}Now that I got a sense of what you do here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想着你能分享下你的想法\N{\fs24\1c}I thought you might have a take on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你熟悉大家 高低贵贱都有\N{\fs24\1c}You know people, high and low.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他们的秘密\N{\fs24\1c}You know their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,严格保密\N{\fs24\1c}Strict confidentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点在夜车里有保障\N{\fs24\1c}It's assured in the Nightcar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欣赏这点\N{\fs24\1c}I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:09:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮·卡维尔跟你聊过吗\N{\fs24\1c}Melanie Cavill ever have a session?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算答案是肯定的\N{\fs24\1c}That would be confidential --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是保密信息\N{\fs24\1c}if the answer wasn't no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她从未那样暴露过自己\N{\fs24\1c}She's never shown herself like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许现在她必须如此了\N{\fs24\1c}Maybe now she'll have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得妮基的死可能成为催化剂吗\N{\fs24\1c}Think Nikki's death could be a catalyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么的催化剂\N{\fs24\1c}Catalyst for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据我所知 三等厢的工人们都受够了\N{\fs24\1c}From what I hear, a lot of workers in Third are pretty fed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得步步为营 警探\N{\fs24\1c}You need to step carefully, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:27.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们很多人确实想改变\N{\fs24\1c}But many of us do want change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要叫醒头等厢了\N{\fs24\1c}We're waking First.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥德丽 我保证会尽全力\N{\fs24\1c}Audrey, I promise I'll do everything I can --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:40.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话了 梅兰妮\N{\fs24\1c}Cut the shit, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我支持你 警探\N{\fs24\1c}You have my support, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会控制附属列车\N{\fs24\1c}I'm holding the subtrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列车后方没多少人相信当权者\N{\fs24\1c}Not a lot of downtrain faith that the powers that be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:10:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的想破这起案子\N{\fs24\1c}actually want to solve this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为嫌犯是头等厢的人\N{\fs24\1c}now that the suspect's from First.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想破\N{\fs24\1c}I want it solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.48,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管凶手来自哪个车厢\N{\fs24\1c}And it doesn't matter which Class the suspect is from.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs24\1c}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没见过蓝色芯片\N{\fs24\1c}I've never seen a blue chip before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是头等厢的 开各种车门\N{\fs24\1c}Could be First Class, open heaps of doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿说 "我们之间只隔了几扇门"\N{\fs24\1c}Layton said, "It's only doors between us."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能用芯片走出车尾\N{\fs24\1c}You can't just chip out of the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 但可以离开清洁小队\N{\fs24\1c}No, but someone could chip out of Sanitation crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息室\N{\fs24\1c}Ah, the break room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有扇带键盘的门\N{\fs24\1c}There's that door with the key pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们认为我们不能用\N{\fs24\1c}They think we can't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里藏了物资 对吧\N{\fs24\1c}You've been stashing supplies there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我们当班时搜索来的东西\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah. Things we scrounge on shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有衣服吗 -有\N{\fs24\1c}- Any clothes? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 如果我们能让人进入走廊 然后呢\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, so, if we get someone in the corridors, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们和阿斯特丽德取得联系\N{\fs24\1c}We make contact with Astrid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙 自从她第一年出去当学徒\N{\fs24\1c}Since she apprenticed out in the first year,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:43.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有过几次她的消息 两次吗\N{\fs24\1c}guys, we've heard from her, what, twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯特丽德还是我们的一员\N{\fs24\1c}Astrid's still one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在这里有人\N{\fs24\1c}She's got people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是她能找到莱顿 我们就能和他建立联系\N{\fs24\1c}If she can find Layton, we can set up communication with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把芯片给我\N{\fs24\1c}Give me the chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚试试\N{\fs24\1c}I'll try tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰 你是一头雄狮\N{\fs24\1c}John, you're a lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在前列车厢不常看到车尾女人\N{\fs24\1c}They don't see Tailie women uptrain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我混进去的几率更高\N{\fs24\1c}I've got a better chance of blending in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的\N{\fs24\1c}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们拿到的唯一一把钥匙\N{\fs24\1c}This is the only key we've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清洁\N{\fs24\1c}Sanitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你朋友呢\N{\fs24\1c}Hey, what happened to your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他病得太重没法工作 长官\N{\fs24\1c}Uh, he's too sick to work, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs24\1c}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 这边\N{\fs24\1c}Come on. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服脱掉\N{\fs24\1c}Strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不人道\N{\fs24\1c}It's inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在逗我吧\N{\fs24\1c}You got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艺术现在属于头等厢吗\N{\fs24\1c}Art belongs to First now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这帮人先把大地烤焦 再将其冰封\N{\fs24\1c}These people broiled the Earth, then they froze her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在又把战利品挂在他们的墙上\N{\fs24\1c}and now they hang the spoils on their walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱顿 我出生在宾州东部的泥泞农场上\N{\fs24\1c}Layton, I was a born on a dirt farm in Eastern Pennsylvania.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我白手起家\N{\fs24\1c}I came from nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对阶级概念略知一二\N{\fs24\1c}I know a thing or two about class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到这一切时感受到的愤怒\N{\fs24\1c}That anger that you feel when you look at all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是合理的\N{\fs24\1c}It's justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要利用它\N{\fs24\1c}Let's use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.33,0:14:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论凶手是谁\N{\fs24\1c}Whoever the killer is,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头等厢都会保护自己人\N{\fs24\1c}First is going to protect their own,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.56,0:14:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就做他们最可怕的车尾噩梦\N{\fs24\1c}so you be their worst nightmare from the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他交给我\N{\fs24\1c}I'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车尾人\N{\fs24\1c}Tailie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 先说两件事\N{\fs24\1c}Alright, two things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎你们是谁\N{\fs24\1c}I don't give a shit who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这里有人喜欢\N{\fs24\1c}and somebody up here has got a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切掉三等厢乘客的老二\N{\fs24\1c}for chopping off Third Class dicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听着 -我在听呢\N{\fs24\1c}- Now, look-- - Yeah, I'm looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的\N{\fs24\1c}Here's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝\N{\fs24\1c}Ruth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看搏击的人没到齐\N{\fs24\1c}I don't see everybody who was at the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都在这儿了\N{\fs24\1c}This is everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅兰妮 这太荒唐了\N{\fs24\1c}Melanie, this is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头等厢还没人被定过罪\N{\fs24\1c}No one from First Class has ever been charged with a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你得感谢她\N{\fs24\1c}You should thank her for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她严守边境 把乌合之众拒之门外\N{\fs24\1c}She keeps the borders tight, she keeps the rabble at bay,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让头等厢凌驾于法律之上\N{\fs24\1c}and she keeps First Class above the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但威尔福德先生这次行事不同往常\N{\fs24\1c}But Mr. Wilford's doing things differently this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.94,0:15:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是这样\N{\fs24\1c}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs24\1c}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs24\1c}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保镖在哪里\N{\fs24\1c}...where are the bodyguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:15:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 那我换种方式\N{\fs24\1c}Alright, let me try this a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在车尾断了多少只手臂\N{\fs24\1c}How many arms did you take in the Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,14只 如果有人数了的话\N{\fs24\1c}14, if anyone's counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 保镖在哪里\N{\fs24\1c}So, where are the bodyguards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我找佣人来的\N{\fs24\1c}I didn't invite the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克昨晚没有回家\N{\fs24\1c}Erik didn't come home last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没回吗\N{\fs24\1c}He didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs24\1c}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要求提前离开搏击之夜\N{\fs24\1c}He asked to leave the fight early,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我们回来时 他不在这里\N{\fs24\1c}and when we came back, he wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他不见了 但却没有告诉我们\N{\fs24\1c}You knew he was missing and you didn't tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉罗切 埃里克是嫌疑犯\N{\fs24\1c}Tell Roche Erik's a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他身上还带着枪\N{\fs24\1c}He has his gun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-小莱 -小莱\N{\fs24\1c}- LJ. - LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs24\1c}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨晚看到他带着枪了\N{\fs24\1c}I saw he had it with him last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还有枪吗\N{\fs24\1c}He has his gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪国列车上不允许持枪\N{\fs24\1c}There are no guns allowed on the Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的保安是可以携带随身武器的\N{\fs24\1c}Our security was allowed to keep their sidearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们其他人却被没收武器来确保你们的安全\N{\fs24\1c}The rest of us were disarmed to keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去看一下埃里克的住处\N{\fs24\1c}I'm gonna need to see Erik's quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人不能进入我们的车厢\N{\fs24\1c}This man is not entering our carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把这个人带进头等厢吗\N{\fs24\1c}Bringing this man into First?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这从来没发生过\N{\fs24\1c}This is unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代表这里的所有人\N{\fs24\1c}On behalf of everyone here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求和威尔福德先生说话\N{\fs24\1c}I demand to speak to Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在 梅兰妮\N{\fs24\1c}It's time, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是班尼特\N{\fs24\1c}This is Bennett.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我需要你为我接通他的电话\N{\fs24\1c}I'm sorry. I need you to put me through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很紧急\N{\fs24\1c}It's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又要再演一次吗\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, hey, are we doing this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 我等着\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you. I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意做任何让你高兴的事\N{\fs24\1c}Anything to put a smile on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是好消息\N{\fs24\1c}Good news first --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能已经确认凶手了\N{\fs24\1c}we may have identified the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗\N{\fs24\1c}Is that for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说也是在演戏\N{\fs24\1c}Or is that part of the act?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 头等厢的一名保镖\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, a bodyguard from First.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.71,0:18:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那家人不太愿意\N{\fs24\1c}But the family's reluctant
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你的警探进入车厢进行调查\N{\fs24\1c}to let your Detective in to investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想要跟你说句话\N{\fs24\1c}and they would like a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换我也会气坏的\N{\fs24\1c}Well, that would piss me right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怒气冲冲\N{\fs24\1c}Huff, huff, huff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福爵家族\N{\fs24\1c}The Folgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们的人\N{\fs24\1c}It's their man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 莱拉·福爵 先生\N{\fs24\1c}Yes, Lilah Folger, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.43,0:18:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但她强烈要求\N{\fs24\1c}I know, but she's demanding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs24\1c}Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.38,0:18:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了调查 我们允许他进去\N{\fs24\1c}For the investigation, we will allow him in,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.20,0:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但条件是你要陪着他\N{\fs24\1c}but only if you accompany him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生 向您道歉\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎事情都解决了\N{\fs24\1c}It seems everything is sorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你 梅\N{\fs24\1c}I miss you, Mel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:18:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 先生\N{\fs24\1c}Goodbye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十分钟\N{\fs24\1c}30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.93,0:20:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\fs24\1c}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界屎尿都在这儿了\N{\fs24\1c}All the piss and shit left in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你会习惯这味道的 -快 快开始\N{\fs24\1c}- You get used to the smell. - Quick, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-又不是霍乱 -霍乱也不是很糟\N{\fs24\1c}- Just not the cholera. - Cholera's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.74,0:20:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快点 开始吧\N{\fs24\1c}Come on, quick, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁他们还没来\N{\fs24\1c}Before they get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,递给我\N{\fs24\1c}Pass me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡衣\N{\fs24\1c}Pajamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 已经是半夜了\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, it's the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺合适的 是吧\N{\fs24\1c}Kinda works, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.99,0:20:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 搞快点\N{\fs24\1c}It's fine. Better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好 -出发 快点\N{\fs24\1c}- Alright. - Let's go. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把那个给我\N{\fs24\1c}Pass it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fs24\1c}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fs24\1c}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是要检查我们的全部家当吗\N{\fs24\1c}Is he going to go through all of our things?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要再给他点喝的\N{\fs24\1c}Should we offer him a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 谢谢你小莱\N{\fs24\1c}No thanks, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾服役于第七海军陆战队\N{\fs24\1c}He was 7th Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来做了私人保镖\N{\fs24\1c}Then he worked private security.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么其他情况吗\N{\fs24\1c}What else can you tell me about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是在冰封开始时雇佣他的\N{\fs24\1c}We hired him when the Freeze started
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以保证全家人的安全 他也做到了\N{\fs24\1c}to keep our family safe, and he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也救过我的命\N{\fs24\1c}And he saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么救的\N{\fs24\1c}How'd he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.12,0:21:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那与这无关 小莱\N{\fs24\1c}That's not pertinent, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人见过这个吗\N{\fs24\1c}Anybody seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs24\1c}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是把开盖刀\N{\fs24\1c}It's a J-Hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,养蜂用的\N{\fs24\1c}Used for beekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.59,0:21:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 他给我看过 他说是他找到的\N{\fs24\1c}What? He showed it to me. He said he found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-在哪儿找到的 -不知道\N{\fs24\1c}- Where? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捡来的吧\N{\fs24\1c}Scrounging.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在以前的养蜂场吗\N{\fs24\1c}The old Apiary?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.21,0:22:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以前有养蜂\N{\fs24\1c}We used to keep bees
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.73,0:22:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到三年前的一次蜂群衰竭失调\N{\fs24\1c}until a colony collapse three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.31,0:22:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的蜂箱和其余物品都装箱了\N{\fs24\1c}They crated up all the extra hives and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.12,0:22:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存放在仓库里\N{\fs24\1c}They're in storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就得找到那个箱子\N{\fs24\1c}Well, we need to find which crate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能让提尔过来吗\N{\fs24\1c}Can you send Till?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看看吗\N{\fs24\1c}May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱拉 我们去另一个房间\N{\fs24\1c}Lilah, let's us three go into the other room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以商讨一下对你们最有利的处理方式\N{\fs24\1c}We can position this in a way that's best for your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司闸员提尔\N{\fs24\1c}Brakeman Till.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.16,0:23:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔茜\N{\fs24\1c}Josie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎...你从车尾出来了吗\N{\fs24\1c}How -- How did -- Are you out of the Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.47,0:23:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别问 好吗 没时间了\N{\fs24\1c}No questions, okay? There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.58,0:23:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在食品处理部门吗\N{\fs24\1c}Are you still in Food Processing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在 但我只负责切割和装载能量棒\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, but I just cut and load the bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.13,0:23:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能插手配料之类的\N{\fs24\1c}I don't have access to ingredients or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是想要这个\N{\fs24\1c}That's not what we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道莱顿出来了吗\N{\fs24\1c}Did you know that Layton's out?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道 他们让他当警探\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, they're using him as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个杀手逍遥法外\N{\fs24\1c}There's a killer loose up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这样\N{\fs24\1c}That's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.14,0:23:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 听着\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想让你跟他联系\N{\fs24\1c}We need you to make contact with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.24,0:23:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乔茜 如果他们抓到我\N{\fs24\1c}Josie, if they catch me --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能会被送回车尾 我知道\N{\fs24\1c}You could be sent back to the Tail. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我懂\N{\fs24\1c}Honey, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.04,0:23:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在很健康\N{\fs24\1c}You're healthy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你活得像个人样\N{\fs24\1c}You live like a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车尾需要你\N{\fs24\1c}The Tail needs you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要你\N{\fs24\1c}We need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车尾一心\N{\fs24\1c}One Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.41,0:24:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车尾一心\N{\fs24\1c}One Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.35,0:24:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fs24\1c}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.76,0:24:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来埃里克并不是出生就有现在这么好的条件\N{\fs24\1c}Looks like Erik wasn't born into the nice life he had up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.03,0:24:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 他的童年并不美好\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, I don't think he had a very good childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他能干出这种事吗\N{\fs24\1c}You think he was capable of something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.70,0:24:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fs24\1c}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.86,0:24:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他打退了那些\N{\fs24\1c}He sure wasted those rioters
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.97,0:24:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我来雪国列车的路上想抓我的暴徒\N{\fs24\1c}who tried to grab me on the way to Snowpiercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.61,0:24:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是在那时救了你的命吗\N{\fs24\1c}Is that when he saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.53,0:25:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他总开玩笑说自己冷血\N{\fs24\1c}He joked about being cold-blooded.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.70,0:25:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为大冰封而生\N{\fs24\1c}Born for the Freeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.78,0:25:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这真的是埃里克 那也不是我们的错\N{\fs24\1c}Even if this was Erik, it's not our fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.91,0:25:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人说是\N{\fs24\1c}Nobody's saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.85,0:25:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都能想象到会有什么闲话了\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, I can just hear the track talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.82,0:25:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多年来 我们都知道\N{\fs24\1c}Over the years, we learned that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.20,0:25:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克作为列兵 有做过一些事\N{\fs24\1c}as a private soldier, Erik did things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.31,0:25:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他的使命\N{\fs24\1c}It's what he's for.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.94,0:25:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是变态杀手\N{\fs24\1c}Not psychotic murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.88,0:25:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让人以为我们庇护了一个禽兽\N{\fs24\1c}It can't come off like we have sheltered a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.32,0:25:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克有没有在你面前展示出过暴力或古怪的行为\N{\fs24\1c}Did Erik ever get aggressive or...weird with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.64,0:25:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在车尾真的看不到太阳吗\N{\fs24\1c}You guys really not get to see the sun in the Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.75,0:25:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们很多人七年没见过太阳了\N{\fs24\1c}Most of us haven't seen the sun in seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.73,0:25:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你住在这里\N{\fs24\1c}How's that make you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.77,0:25:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受应有尽有的生活 感觉怎么样\N{\fs24\1c}living up here with everything you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.08,0:25:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们自己没有票\N{\fs24\1c}I mean, you guys didn't have tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.04,0:25:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧好了\N{\fs24\1c}Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.62,0:26:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他问了你和埃里克的关系\N{\fs24\1c}He asked about your relationship with Erik.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.22,0:26:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么了\N{\fs24\1c}What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.70,0:26:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会不会和你说什么\N{\fs24\1c}He tell you things?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.59,0:26:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你保守秘密\N{\fs24\1c}Ask you to keep secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.09,0:26:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱\N{\fs24\1c}LJ?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.88,0:26:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我最好不说\N{\fs24\1c}No, I-I better not talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.43,0:27:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能坐下谈谈吗\N{\fs24\1c}Can we sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.77,0:27:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要问你们关于埃里克和小莱的事\N{\fs24\1c}I need to ask you about Erik and LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.90,0:27:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等你的消息 好吗\N{\fs24\1c}We'll expect to hear from you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.34,0:27:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fs24\1c}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.14,0:27:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.88,0:27:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈尔斯\N{\fs24\1c}Miles...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.35,0:27:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克里斯托弗\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, Christopher.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.92,0:27:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和妈妈说说 她会理解的\N{\fs24\1c}Talk to Mom. She'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.12,0:27:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便了\N{\fs24\1c}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.15,0:27:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要迟到了\N{\fs24\1c}She's gonna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.82,0:27:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计 你这样让我很紧张\N{\fs24\1c}Mate, you're stressing me out doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.73,0:27:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两分钟\N{\fs24\1c}Two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.46,0:28:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-总算来了 -嗯\N{\fs24\1c}- 'bout time. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.37,0:28:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣地亚哥要发心脏病了\N{\fs24\1c}Santiago here's about to have a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.64,0:28:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得赶紧走 快点\N{\fs24\1c}We got to move. Faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.22,0:28:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上这个\N{\fs24\1c}Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.97,0:28:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好\N{\fs24\1c}Okay. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.82,0:28:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三 二\N{\fs24\1c}Three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.09,0:28:16.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了 -一\N{\fs24\1c}- There you go. ... - one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.42,0:28:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续工作\N{\fs24\1c}Back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.59,0:28:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 继续工作\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.67,0:28:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们突然\N{\fs24\1c}So, suddenly we're searching for
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.80,0:28:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找一个拿手枪的专业士兵了\N{\fs24\1c}a professional soldier with a pistol?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.08,0:28:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,.38左轮\N{\fs24\1c}Revolver .38.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.21,0:28:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人安心 谢谢\N{\fs24\1c}That's comforting, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.52,0:28:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定他没在上面吗\N{\fs24\1c}Hey, you sure it's not above?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.32,0:28:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就是在这层\N{\fs24\1c}No, it's on this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.81,0:28:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边\N{\fs24\1c}Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.03,0:29:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有人吗\N{\fs24\1c}Anybody in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.87,0:29:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门\N{\fs24\1c}Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.31,0:29:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跑了\N{\fs24\1c}He's on the move!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.49,0:29:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在上边\N{\fs24\1c}He's up top!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.31,0:29:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 站住\N{\fs24\1c}Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.07,0:29:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上上上上\N{\fs24\1c}Go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.04,0:29:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开\N{\fs24\1c}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.19,0:29:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯维勒 抓住他\N{\fs24\1c}Osweiller, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.11,0:29:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上去了\N{\fs24\1c}I'm going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.72,0:29:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又下去了 他去楼梯了\N{\fs24\1c}He's going back down! He's going to the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.71,0:29:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我去追\N{\fs24\1c}Okay! I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.57,0:29:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 让开\N{\fs24\1c}Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.85,0:29:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小奥\N{\fs24\1c}Oz!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.97,0:29:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要跑掉了\N{\fs24\1c}He's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.47,0:29:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs24\1c}Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.45,0:29:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fs24\1c}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.58,0:29:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克只能带两个包上车\N{\fs24\1c}Erik was only allowed two bags on the train,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.76,0:29:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后他带了唱片\N{\fs24\1c}and he brings records.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.44,0:29:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是他爸爸的\N{\fs24\1c}They were his dad's.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.07,0:30:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他恨他爸爸\N{\fs24\1c}He hated his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.18,0:30:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是白人\N{\fs24\1c}He was white.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.70,0:30:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用说\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, no shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.12,0:30:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只猫\N{\fs24\1c}It's a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.24,0:30:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 只是\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah, yeah, I-I know. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.43,0:30:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有段时间没见过了\N{\fs24\1c}It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.81,0:30:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是埃里克救下来的\N{\fs24\1c}Erik saved him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.94,0:30:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它从哪来的\N{\fs24\1c}Where'd he come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.23,0:30:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪皮特是伪装大师\N{\fs24\1c}Snowpeter is a master of disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.64,0:30:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪皮特\N{\fs24\1c}Snowpeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.51,0:30:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真逗\N{\fs24\1c}That's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.40,0:31:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说你们吃人\N{\fs24\1c}I hear you eat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.72,0:31:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不吃了\N{\fs24\1c}We put a stop to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.12,0:31:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs24\1c}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.48,0:31:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让前面的人都害怕你们\N{\fs24\1c}It keeps everyone up here scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.88,0:31:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意为了让所有人惶恐不安而吃人\N{\fs24\1c}Like, I'd eat a dude just to make everyone shit bricks
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.41,0:31:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像他们害怕车尾人一样\N{\fs24\1c}like they do with the Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.23,0:31:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这首歌\N{\fs24\1c}I know this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.44,0:31:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮基·吉奈特也知道\N{\fs24\1c}So did Nikki Genet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.17,0:31:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道\N{\fs24\1c}You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.16,0:31:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对抗这系统的时候\N{\fs24\1c}you're a lot cooler smashing the system
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.74,0:31:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你做威尔福德走狗时酷多了\N{\fs24\1c}than you are being Wilford's dick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.24,0:31:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我们可以两者兼得\N{\fs24\1c}Well, maybe we can do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.28,0:31:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克有跟你说过他用这个做过什么吗\N{\fs24\1c}Erik ever tell you what he did with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.58,0:31:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不可能\N{\fs24\1c}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.75,0:31:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说埃里克养育了小莱\N{\fs24\1c}Erik practically raised LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.82,0:32:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟早会曝光的 莱拉\N{\fs24\1c}It's going to come out, Lilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.96,0:32:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-闭嘴 罗伯特 -不行\N{\fs24\1c}- Zip it, Robert. - We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.38,0:32:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克和小莱很亲密\N{\fs24\1c}Erik and LJ are close.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.84,0:32:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"亲密"\N{\fs24\1c}"Close."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.65,0:32:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法拒绝她\N{\fs24\1c}I can't say no to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.65,0:32:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在当下\N{\fs24\1c}It's these times.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.30,0:32:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道德品行就是个移动靶子\N{\fs24\1c}Morality's a moving target.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.03,0:32:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开门了吗 安东\N{\fs24\1c}You open yet, Anton?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.11,0:32:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来 珍珠 你来了\N{\fs24\1c}Come in, Jinju. You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.31,0:32:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贝丝的礼物在这儿\N{\fs24\1c}I've got Bess' gift right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.75,0:33:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-拜托 -闭嘴 闭嘴\N{\fs24\1c}- Please... - Shut up. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.22,0:33:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一把枪\N{\fs24\1c}A gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.54,0:33:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一把真枪\N{\fs24\1c}An actual gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.01,0:33:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静\N{\fs24\1c}Keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.24,0:33:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就爆了你的头\N{\fs24\1c}Or this artifact will blow your head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.03,0:33:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs24\1c}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.85,0:33:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 我们不想惹麻烦\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, we're -- we don't want any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.50,0:33:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他们不顾我反对\N{\fs24\1c}You know they hauled me up out of the Tail
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.57,0:33:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我从车尾拖出来破这案子吗\N{\fs24\1c}to solve this against my will?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.07,0:33:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事跟我的利益无关\N{\fs24\1c}I got no skin in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.23,0:33:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克或许是凶手 但是移除身体部位\N{\fs24\1c}Erik might've been the murderer, but removing body parts --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.10,0:33:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是因为这个而搞砸了\N{\fs24\1c}that's how he screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.21,0:33:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说搞砸是指什么\N{\fs24\1c}What do you mean he screwed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.80,0:33:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阉割是激情犯罪\N{\fs24\1c}Well, castration's a crime of passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.56,0:33:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个女人惩罚男人的措施\N{\fs24\1c}A punishment that women lay down on men.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.16,0:33:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是他的主意 对吗\N{\fs24\1c}That wasn't his idea, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.46,0:33:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他多半只是在帮他人\N{\fs24\1c}He's probably just controlling the victim
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.24,0:33:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制受害者 对吗\N{\fs24\1c}for somebody else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.55,0:33:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要放你的歌吗\N{\fs24\1c}So, are we playing your song?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.95,0:34:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我是个蓝眼睛头等厢女孩\N{\fs24\1c}Shit, if I was a blue-eyed Firstie girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.40,0:34:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会想要拖延时间\N{\fs24\1c}I'd be playing for time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.45,0:34:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克会死得很壮烈 对吗\N{\fs24\1c}Erik's going down in a blaze of glory, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.90,0:34:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会进抽屉\N{\fs24\1c}He's not going to The Drawers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.82,0:34:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人说出去\N{\fs24\1c}So, no one tells.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.98,0:34:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你终于能感觉到什么\N{\fs24\1c}And you finally got to feel something.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.78,0:34:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他为你按住那些男人的时候\N{\fs24\1c}When he held those men down for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.66,0:34:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咔嚓\N{\fs24\1c}Chop, chop.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.93,0:35:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假设你说对了2%\N{\fs24\1c}Say you were even 2% right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.34,0:35:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车尾人需要东西\N{\fs24\1c}Tailies need stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.28,0:35:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是在四处搜寻\N{\fs24\1c}Always scrounging.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.18,0:35:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定想要设计图吧\N{\fs24\1c}Bet you'd like blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.14,0:35:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能要枪吗\N{\fs24\1c}How about guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.31,0:35:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有头等厢安保人员有\N{\fs24\1c}Only First Class security gets those.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.93,0:35:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说真的\N{\fs24\1c}You really are serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.98,0:35:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我打赌一个蓝眼睛头等厢女孩\N{\fs24\1c}But I bet a blue-eyed Firstie girl
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.27,0:35:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许能搞到枪\N{\fs24\1c}might be able to get her hands on one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.35,0:35:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要守口如瓶就行吗\N{\fs24\1c}And all I got to do is tell nobody?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.45,0:35:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就在这里某个地方 我们在门口安排了守卫\N{\fs24\1c}He's somewhere in here. We got jackboots on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.10,0:35:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 各位 我们要扩大封锁范围\N{\fs24\1c}Alright, folks, we're extending lockdown right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.75,0:35:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说过会这样的\N{\fs24\1c}She said this was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.06,0:35:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fs24\1c}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.62,0:36:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的女人吗\N{\fs24\1c}Your girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.57,0:36:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听好\N{\fs24\1c}Alright, folks, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.29,0:36:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照我说的做\N{\fs24\1c}Just do what I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.55,0:36:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下 快\N{\fs24\1c}Get down. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.03,0:36:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刷芯片 刷芯片\N{\fs24\1c}Chip in. Chip in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.93,0:36:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs24\1c}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.25,0:36:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去 下去\N{\fs24\1c}Down. Down, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.66,0:36:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌疑犯在那\N{\fs24\1c}There's the suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.75,0:36:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在下面 有一个人质\N{\fs24\1c}He's down below, one hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.40,0:36:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到我们这边来\N{\fs24\1c}Push down towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.52,0:36:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs24\1c}Go. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.99,0:36:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你的名字\N{\fs24\1c}Just tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.70,0:36:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这重要吗\N{\fs24\1c}Does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.25,0:37:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\fs24\1c}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.65,0:37:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fs24\1c}They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.55,0:37:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包抄\N{\fs24\1c}Alright, flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.02,0:37:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过去\N{\fs24\1c}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.23,0:37:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过去\N{\fs24\1c}Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.50,0:37:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跪下\N{\fs24\1c}Kneel down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.33,0:37:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前\N{\fs24\1c}Forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.95,0:37:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 我们不能轻举妄动\N{\fs24\1c}No, no! We have -- We have to hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.47,0:37:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后 他会开枪打她的\N{\fs24\1c}Hey, pull back. He'll shoot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.94,0:37:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下棍子\N{\fs24\1c}Batons down!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.73,0:37:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把武器都放下 快\N{\fs24\1c}Weapons on the deck, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.35,0:37:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲\N{\fs24\1c}Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.78,0:38:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我接通梅兰妮·卡维尔 很紧急\N{\fs24\1c}Get me Melanie Cavill. It's urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.36,0:38:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fs24\1c}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.56,0:38:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克死了\N{\fs24\1c}Erik's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.13,0:38:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在呢 宝贝 我在\N{\fs24\1c}I got you, baby. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.45,0:38:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs24\1c}Sweetie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.37,0:38:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs24\1c}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.45,0:39:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我在\N{\fs24\1c}I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.87,0:39:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.99,0:39:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fs24\1c}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.56,0:39:35.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况\N{\fs24\1c}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.10,0:39:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃里克只是听命行事的走狗\N{\fs24\1c}Erik was a dog who did what he was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.41,0:39:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱拉叫他折磨\N{\fs24\1c}And Lilah Junior told him to torture
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.29,0:39:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并杀害了两个三等厢乘客\N{\fs24\1c}and kill two Third Class men.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.66,0:39:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs24\1c}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.83,0:39:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你女儿是杀人犯\N{\fs24\1c}Your daughter's a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.97,0:39:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-放肆 -什么\N{\fs24\1c}- How dare you! - What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.45,0:39:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不 小莱 不\N{\fs24\1c}No, no, LJ, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.53,0:39:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小莱 住手 不\N{\fs24\1c}LJ, stop it! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.86,0:39:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs24\1c}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.10,0:40:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要 不\N{\fs24\1c}No! No! No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.14,0:40:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我的宝贝\N{\fs24\1c}Leave my baby alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.28,0:40:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你立刻放开她\N{\fs24\1c}You get off of her right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.93,0:40:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有乘客请注意\N{\fs24\1c}Attention all passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.17,0:40:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我代表威尔福德先生\N{\fs24\1c}On behalf of Mr. Wilford,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.58,0:40:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与各位分享这一消息\N{\fs24\1c}I share this news --
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.33,0:40:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾藏匿于我们之中的谋杀犯已死\N{\fs24\1c}the murderer who hid among us is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.18,0:40:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二名嫌犯已被关押\N{\fs24\1c}and a second suspect is in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.92,0:40:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了成功的调查\N{\fs24\1c}Thanks to a successful investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.09,0:40:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秩序得以恢复\N{\fs24\1c}order has been restored,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.44,0:40:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生向各位保证 正义必胜\N{\fs24\1c}and Mr. Wilford assures you justice will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.20,0:41:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德工业全体员工感谢你们\N{\fs24\1c}From all of us at Wilford Industries, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.96,0:41:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在威尔福德先生必须伸张正义\N{\fs24\1c}Now Mr. Wilford has to deliver justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.13,0:41:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那承诺也是由你负责吗\N{\fs24\1c}You in charge of that promise, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.43,0:41:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我请你喝一杯 警探\N{\fs24\1c}How about I buy you a drink, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.69,0:41:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很美 不是吗\N{\fs24\1c}Beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.23,0:41:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs24\1c}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.06,0:41:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类统治和资源控制的纪念碑\N{\fs24\1c}A monument to human dominion and resource control.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.03,0:41:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦\N{\fs24\1c}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.88,0:41:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把政治放一边 好好庆祝胜利\N{\fs24\1c}Let's put the politics down and celebrate a win.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.55,0:41:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去 是清酒\N{\fs24\1c}Oh, shit. Sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.80,0:42:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为威尔福德先生的大秘密是什么\N{\fs24\1c}What do you think Mr. Wilford's big secret even was?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.60,0:42:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想回车尾 梅兰妮\N{\fs24\1c}I just want to go back to the Tail, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.06,0:42:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我不能放你回去\N{\fs24\1c}You know I can't let you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.23,0:42:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见了太多\N{\fs24\1c}You've seen too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.28,0:42:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经想到了 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}You figured it out, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.12,0:42:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs24\1c}I know you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.42,0:42:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神话具有强大的力量\N{\fs24\1c}A myth's a powerful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.17,0:42:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你永远不知道它的重量\N{\fs24\1c}Pray you never know the weight of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.40,0:43:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 莱顿\N{\fs24\1c}I'm sorry, Layton.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.96,0:43:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢 -注意保暖 兄弟\N{\fs24\1c}- Thank you. - Keep warm, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.59,0:43:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 等一下\N{\fs24\1c}Hang on. Hang on, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.34,0:43:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 里面没东西\N{\fs24\1c}Okay, nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.72,0:43:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你\N{\fs24\1c}There you go, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.43,0:43:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉美\N{\fs24\1c}Yoshimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.58,0:43:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一如既往地迷人\N{\fs24\1c}You're looking stunning as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.98,0:43:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么...\N{\fs24\1c}What the --
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.04,0:43:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\fs24\1c}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.17,0:43:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你替我\N{\fs24\1c}Take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.21,0:44:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-乔茜 -他在干什么\N{\fs24\1c}- Hey, Josie! - What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.21,0:44:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我过去\N{\fs24\1c}Coming through, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.63,0:44:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心碰头 让一让\N{\fs24\1c}Mind your head. Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.55,0:44:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fs24\1c}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.16,0:44:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来阿斯特丽德兑现了承诺\N{\fs24\1c}Looks like Astrid came through.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.74,0:44:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-太好了 -是啊\N{\fs24\1c}- Yes. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.92,0:44:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}莱顿失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.70,0:44:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别登记他\N{\fs24\1c}Keep him off-book.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.46,0:44:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 医生\N{\fs24\1c}And, Doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.68,0:44:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威尔福德先生不希望他受到损伤\N{\fs24\1c}Mr. Wilford does not want him damaged.
